			<h2 class="heading-section__heading">Alternate routes</h2>
			<h3>Direct entry to second year</h3> 

			<p>If you have excellent qualifications, you may be able to apply for <a href="https://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/subjects/biology/biology-bsc/direct/">direct entry to second year</a>. This allows you to bypass first-year modules and complete your degree in only three years instead of four. </p>  
			<h3>Integrated Masters</h3> 

			<p>Integrated Masters courses allow you to combine undergraduate and postgraduate study into a single five-year programme and graduate with a Masters degree. St Andrews offers the <a href="https://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/subjects/biology/biology-mbiol-2022/">Biology MBiol integrated Masters programme</a>.</p>  
		</section>
		
