				<li>teachers</li>
				<li>forensic scientists</li>
				<li>management consultants</li>
				<li>marketing and advertising experts.</li>  
			</ul>
			<p>The University has a dedicated <a href="https://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/careers/">Careers Centre</a> which can provide advice and support throughout your degree and beyond to help you build your employability skills.</p>
